<plot>What would you do if the woman you fell in love with simultaneously fell in lust with your best friend, who couldn't care less about her? How far would you go to prove your love to her? These are some of the questions DERRICK PARKS (Lil Zane Copeland) must answer when he meets the beautiful AUTUMN SUMMERS (Sundy Carter) in this light hearted tale of love at first sight. Set on the back drop of historical city of Philadelphia in the beautiful season of Autumn.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?025061</url></doc>
